    Get Flashrom From Cloud
    Execute Linux Command    flashrom -p internal -r coreboot.rom --fmap -i FMAP -i SMMSTORE &> /dev/null
    SSHLibrary.Get File    coreboot.rom    dcu/coreboot.rom
